'''Themba Zwane''', also known as '''Mshishi''' (born 3 August 1989) is a South African professional [[Association football|soccer]] player who plays as an [[Midfielder#Attacking midfielder|attacking midfielder]] for [[Premier Soccer League]] club [[Mamelodi Sundowns F.C.|Mamelodi Sundowns]] and the [[South Africa national soccer team|South Africa national team]].

On the 11th of October 2024 he earned his [[Cap (sport)|50th international cap]] for [[South Africa national soccer team|South Africa]].<ref>{{Cite web |date=2024-10-11 |title=Bafana Bafana's midfield maestro getting his flowers with 50th cap in the offing {{!}} soccer |url=https://www.sabcsport.com/soccer/news/bafana-bafana-s-midfield-maestro-getting-his-flowers-with-50th-cap-in-the-offering |access-date=2024-10-11 |website=SABC |language=en}}</ref>

